y, but winpty fails when there's no TTY\n      if [[ \"$OSTYPE\" == \"msys\" ]] || [[ \"$OSTYPE\" == \"cygwin\" ]]; then\n        alias | grep -v \"='winp"...], 0x4d0d9b02a10 /* 31 vars */ <unfinished ...>
